        "type": "message",
        "text": "A lot of what <@U027RNU0A69> and <@U017WRJTKF1> have said. My team is pretty fortunate that we directly impact revenue considering we don’t have a sales team. So our metrics are really around quality signups rather than traffic, rankings, etc.\n\nWe’ve historically only measured weekly company signups as marketings metric, however we’re working on diving into a bit more detail into things like:\n• % that are on target (i.e. how many of those signups fit our ICP)\n• % that come back on day 2, Day 7, etc\n• % that upgrade to paid users\n• Monthly revenue that comes from each cohort (including expansion) \n• CAC per week, salaries included",
